Package com.enterprise_architecture.essential.importutility.service

Class Summary
DUPImportJob Import Job that is responsible for managing the generation of a DUP from the specified import activity.
DUPImportService Servlet that provides a REST Service interface to the Import Utility, enabling existing Import Activities to be invoked automatically, to create and run a DUP on the EIP platform.
DUPImportServiceImpl Class to implement the DUP service.
ImportJob Class to manage an import task.
ImportResponse Class to manage the callback requests to clients of the service.
ImportService Servlet that provides a REST Service interface to the Import Utility, enabling existing Import Activities to be invoked automatically.
ImportServiceCallbackClient Default callback client for the Import Service.
ImportServiceImpl Class to implement the service.
XmlImportJob Class to manage an XML import task.
XmlImportService Servlet that provides a REST Service interface to the Import Utility, enabling XML Import Activities to be invoked automatically.
XmlImportServiceImpl Class to implement the XML Import service.
